Package etf.dotsandboxes.bb170011d.graphics

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameBoardObject
    Interface representing a single game board object
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Edge
    Represents an edge on the GameBoard which a player can play as a move
    GameBoard
    Container abstraction for the game board Contains Vertices, Edges, PlayerNodes Contains utility methods for game playing
    GamePanel
    Represents a panel for the game Contains the relevant information for the current game and the GameBoard
    MainPanel
    Represents a panel for the main part of the game Contains all the other panels - menu, game, settings
    MenuPanel
    Represents a menu panel for the game Contains options for changing the current active panel
    PlayerNode
    Represents the current state of the node on the GameBoard which is assigned to a player When this node is assigned to a player, the player gets a point
    SettingsPanel
    Represents a panel for the Settings of the game Sets the parameters of the game when active panel is changed
    Vertex
    Dummy class used for Vertex painting
